{"word":"σῶμα","slug":"σῶμα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n102000\" key=\"sw=ma\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">σῶμα</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ατος</itype><foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">, τό</foreign> (<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arc.\">Arc.</a></author> </bibl> dat. pl. <sense id=\"n102000.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">σωμάτεσι</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ IG\">IG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5(2).357.156</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (Stymphalus, <date TEIform=\"date\">iii B.C.</date>)), <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">body</tr_> of man or beast, but in <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author></bibl>, as <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aristarch.</author> </bibl> remarks (v. <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Apollon.\">Apollon.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lex.\">Lex.</a></title_> </bibl>), always <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">dead body, corpse</tr_> (whereas the living body is <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">δέμας</foreign>)<cit TEIform=\"cit\"><quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">, ὥς τε λέων ἐχάρη μεγάλῳ ἐπὶ σώματι κύρσας</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:23\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.23</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:18:161\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TE